## 1. Gin (создание, сканирование, сравнение операций)

1.1 
``` sql
CREATE INDEX IF NOT EXISTS idx_co_notes_fts_gin
ON client_order
USING GIN (to_tsvector('simple', coalesce(notes, '')));

EXPLAIN (ANALYZE, BUFFERS)
SELECT id, notes
FROM client_order
WHERE to_tsvector('simple', coalesce(notes, '')) @@ to_tsquery('simple', 'oil');
```
